{"tid":1555584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不安已] 我係SOGO馬路聽到有關女示威者既對話","createTime":"2019-09-09T11:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:47:38.000Z","uid":149922,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d76a67922d98860de693c4db6395a9c1bc3877","tid":1555584,"uid":149922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"話說我啱啱係SOGO買完四喜月餅，1859左右，當我打算過馬路果陣我聽到一段對話<br />\n<br />\n冇啦啦聽到有人講自由閪係個term又講得好L大聲，咁我本身聽緊歌咁熄左首歌聽下佢地講乜<br />\n<br />\n屌，好撚不安<br />\n<br />\n有三個中年呀叔<br />\n<br />\nA: 自由閪呀嘛 賣國賊 <br />\n<br />\nB/C 冇答佢<br />\n<br />\nA: 屌 啲曱甴 啲警察捉住佢地輪流屌係真架<br />\n<br />\nB呀叔笑一笑<br />\n<br />\nA: 你唔撚信呀 有個黑社會大佬租埋劏房比佢地 因住d自由閪 上去輪流屌<br />\n<br />\nC:  咁巴閉 你晤去？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我聽到依到就再聽唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住 我醒起前幾日灣仔有單劏房火燭 然後我睇返單新聞 送院係兩個男人黎 如果係真 屌 我真係唔撚知點撚樣"},{"pid":"e8e66d4dc2011df926e5fa5587bb3fc5f2008ee1","tid":1555584,"uid":222451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"庫爾德戰士憶ISIS駁火場面嘆香港如中東戰場：警察怎能把市民當恐怖分子？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555473\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555473</a>"},{"pid":"60f39a67b3a6c909707307c28d39d238709c4d50","tid":1555584,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"up 乜鳩"},{"pid":"1e23692dc9b30c94c90ebd87c92db820d94db319","tid":1555584,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"ba4d2b45710bef6acd4912644b320fe5f06d5c2e","tid":1555584,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"block得 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"f2409e02f0a0b1ecd042711c8dd8d049c4ace4ea","tid":1555584,"uid":262489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"我唔明"}]}